 think the greatest breakthrough each and everyone of us need is not on finance, marriage, work, relationship, own house, car but self. The first breakthrough should start from being selfish.', 7734, 0), (50424, 'Is it not funny, in the presence of an unlimited God, we will still be stucked? Sometimes faith overwrites the fact, that some people have not come to realise. Stop giving excuses and telling God what is happening around you. You have the tools.', 7734, 0), (50425, 'There is no where that life problem can take you that God''s presence cannot reach you. There is nothing that people can do to you that can keep God from getting to you.', 7734, 0), (50426, 'You have a standing invitation to experience God''s presence but you have to pay attention because attention creates access.', 7734, 0), (50427, 'The reason some people do not experience God in their life is the same reason that we do not notice that something is going wrong with our marriage untill we arrive in a divorce court or that something is wrong with our child until we got a phone call from the police station . Simply put....Because we do not pay attention', 7734, 0), (50428, 'When I call on God, I am not trying to get his attention and I am not trying to get Him to notice me. In all this my journey with Him two questions usually comes to my mind, they are; am I paying attention to him or am I trying to get his attention?', 7734, 0), (50429, 'Sometimes we are asking God to reveal his presence, provisions and purpose in our lives and we pray like we are trying to get God''s attention but I think prayer has less with getting God''s attention but He getting mine.', 7734, 0), (50430, 'Evil is real but God is greater.', 7734, 0), (50431, 'God always have a perfect way for every imperfect situations.', 7734, 0), (50432, 'Could it be that while you are waiting for God to come down and help you, God is also waiting for you to get up? Maybe your breakthrough never happen when your situation changes but when 